1
00:00:05,990 --> 00:00:08,633
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,633 --> 00:00:12,188
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,188 --> 00:00:18,281
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,281 --> 00:00:24,507
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,507 --> 00:00:31,028
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,028 --> 00:00:36,014
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,014 --> 00:00:43,214
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,214 --> 00:00:48,338
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,338 --> 00:00:49,851
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,851 --> 00:00:55,614
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,614 --> 00:01:02,214
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,214 --> 00:01:08,581
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,581 --> 00:01:11,817
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:15,059
All right, Xiaowen. Stop crying. Look.

15
00:01:15,059 --> 00:01:17,820
Mommy will do a magic trick for you.

16
00:01:17,820 --> 00:01:19,600
Is that fun?

17
00:01:22,740 --> 00:01:24,040
Xiaowen.

18
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,979
Xiaowen, look who's here?

19
00:01:26,979 --> 00:01:29,903
Who is this? Who is this?

20
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:33,939
Can he say "Daddy" yet?

21
00:01:33,939 --> 00:01:36,319
Wenjing, it's been tough on you.

22
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:39,499
Here, I'll give you a rubber ducky, okay?

23
00:01:39,499 --> 00:01:43,220
Xiaowen, look, a rubber ducky.

24
00:01:43,922 --> 00:01:48,139
[Episode 6: You Feel, I Feel, He Feels...]

25
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,750
Why did you slap me?

26
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:48,800
Are you awake?

27
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,339
What do you mean awake? I'm not asleep.

28
00:02:51,339 --> 00:02:53,919
Mr. Gao said you sleepwalk.

29
00:02:55,650 --> 00:02:57,359
What sleepwalking?

30
00:02:57,359 --> 00:03:00,939
Let me tell you, the temperature varies drastically from morning to night in Tieyuan.

31
00:03:00,939 --> 00:03:02,915
You should cover yourself with a blanket properly.

32
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,400
Otherwise, you'll catch a cold and infect me.

33
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,680
Boss, give me a pancake with eggs and tenderloin.

34
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,779
Extra sauce, please.

35
00:03:25,779 --> 00:03:27,459
Sure.

36
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:32,199
Kancho!

37
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:36,319
Put your hand down!

38
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:38,118
Are you okay?

39
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:44,680
Beibei, if you don't discipline your little brother, he'll get into big trouble in the future.

40
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:47,520
Don't touch him!

41
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:52,059
It's okay. Caress the hair, don't be scared.

42
00:03:52,059 --> 00:03:53,520
Beibei, what happened to you?

43
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,879
You were so happy when I smacked him before.

44
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:58,980
What are you saying? This is my dearest little brother.

45
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:01,937
If you dare to lay your hands on him, I will kill you!

46
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:06,160
It's okay, Doudou. I love you.

47
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:08,680
Sis, what's wrong with you?

48
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:11,260
Us being brother and sister is fate.

49
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:14,459
I will be nice to you for the rest of your life.

50
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:21,959
Slow down! Watch out for the traffic!

51
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:24,260
Beibei, did you take the wrong medicine?

52
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:26,008
Get lost!

53
00:04:26,008 --> 00:04:29,239
From now on, I want to be a generous woman.

54
00:04:29,239 --> 00:04:31,538
Why?

55
00:04:31,538 --> 00:04:36,460
If Gao Yang can accept Xiaowen, why can't I accept Doudou?

56
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:40,380
Beibei, we should be more open-minded. Move.

57
00:04:40,380 --> 00:04:42,600
Who's pancake is this?

58
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,339
Beibei, I bought you breakfast!

59
00:04:44,339 --> 00:04:46,560
Thanks, Bao!

60
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,185
I...

61
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,460
Xiaowen,

62
00:04:52,460 --> 00:04:54,700
why didn't you wake me up for school?

63
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,820
Look, I even bought you breakfast.

64
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:58,360
- Do you want to eat it?
- No thanks.

65
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,759
Eat it.

66
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:04,000
There's an egg and sausage. Try it. Come on.

67
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,820
- Xiaowen, wait for me.
- Morning, Meng.

68
00:05:05,820 --> 00:05:08,650
Wait for me. That pancake was really delicious.

69
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:10,819
If you want to eat it, I'll buy you another one.

70
00:05:10,819 --> 00:05:12,240
Wait a minute.

71
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,982
What?

72
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:25,957
Sit down.

73
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,085
Wait a minute.

74
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:38,300
What now?

75
00:06:05,860 --> 00:06:07,190
[Pull]

76
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,714
How is it?

77
00:06:10,090 --> 00:06:11,840
What is the meaning of this?

78
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:14,905
Freedom. Freedom.

79
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:22,059
Let me tell you. When the teacher is on the podium, and you're in here,

80
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:24,279
he won't be able to see you.

81
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:25,839
What's wrong with Gao Yang?

82
00:06:25,839 --> 00:06:29,619
He has grown up. He's a real man.

83
00:06:29,619 --> 00:06:33,439
You can play games and read comics here.

84
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,680
If you're hungry, you can eat snacks too.

85
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,519
You can do whatever you want.

86
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:41,903
There are all kinds of recreational activities.

87
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:47,219
What do you think? Am I nice to you?

88
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:49,240
Why are you being nice to me?

89
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:51,620
Do you need a reason to be nice to someone? No.

90
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,620
Besides, we're sharing a bunk bed.

91
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:56,401
How's it any different than being real brothers?

92
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,092
I don't need it.

93
00:07:01,092 --> 00:07:03,979
Seriously! Where are you going?

94
00:07:03,979 --> 00:07:06,680
Why did he lose his temper?

95
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:19,839
Ms. Yang, here, try this. I braised this meat this morning.

96
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:21,380
Try it. It's not greasy.

97
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:23,107
- I'll try some then.
- Try it.

98
00:07:23,107 --> 00:07:24,600
Mr. Wu.

99
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,722
Who is it?

100
00:07:26,722 --> 00:07:29,475
X-Xiaowen. What's the matter?

101
00:07:29,475 --> 00:07:32,060
What's Mr. Gao like?

102
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:35,099
He's a pretty nice and upright person.

103
00:07:35,099 --> 00:07:38,839
He's not a local. He came from the neighboring city, Guanping.

104
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:42,219
His parents both work for state-owned enterprises. He grew up in an affluent family.

105
00:07:42,219 --> 00:07:47,580
He looks handsome, doesn't he? He's a college graduate and is good at sports.

106
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:50,140
He even got medals from provincial track and field events.

107
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,620
He was really popular when he just started working.

108
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:55,980
Even though he was really popular, he's an upright person.

109
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:58,900
He didn't fool around at all.

110
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:02,360
I... That's what I admire the most about him.

111
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:05,760
Why? Because I'm the same way, too.

112
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:07,519
We're just... decent.

113
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:09,600
It's only been a few years since I transferred to No. 3 High School.

114
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:12,139
I'm not very familiar with his past.

115
00:08:12,139 --> 00:08:17,259
I just heard... I heard he used to be really handsome.

116
00:08:17,259 --> 00:08:19,700
He was a celebrity in No. 3 High School.

117
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:22,857
Female teachers who had a crush on him could form a line.

118
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,439
But not anymore.

119
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:28,240
After his divorce, he hasn't been taking his work seriously.

120
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:31,559
He has no ambition, and can't even write a lesson plan properly.

121
00:08:31,559 --> 00:08:35,279
His personal life is a mess, too.

122
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:38,119
He doesn't seem like a teacher at all.

123
00:08:38,119 --> 00:08:41,279
Us younger teachers are actually not very close with Mr. Gao.

124
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:46,479
He rarely comes into contact with others and stays in the equipment room all the time.

125
00:08:46,479 --> 00:08:48,659
It's not my place to address it with him.

126
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:54,100
I just know Mr. Gao is divorced and he's on bad terms with his ex-wife.

127
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:56,440
His relationship with Gao Yang isn't great either.

128
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,600
But Principal Jin really favors him.

129
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:01,879
I think Principal Jin knows him much better than we do.

130
00:09:02,958 --> 00:09:07,256
[Principal's Office]

131
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:27,860
Xiaowen, why are you here?

132
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:31,640
I... just happened to pass by.

133
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:35,059
Just in time. I need to talk to you about something. Come in.

134
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:45,240
Here, Xiaowen, have some tea.

135
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,958
Thank you, Principal.

136
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:57,519
I heard you've been asking about Mr. Gao at school lately.

137
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,559
He's actually a very simple man.

138
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:06,472
He's even more simple in romantic relationships.

139
00:10:06,472 --> 00:10:08,559
No matter what rumors you heard,

140
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:12,200
I swear on my honor that they are not true.

141
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:15,100
Mr. Gao was the one who spread the rumors, right?

142
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:18,319
No, no. Mr. Gao didn't spread the rumors.

143
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:24,740
Xiaowen, I want to apologize to you.

144
00:10:24,740 --> 00:10:29,600
When I was having a private conversation with my wife, Beibei accidentally overheard us.

145
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:33,220
As a result, Beibei just gossiped

146
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:37,459
and blindly spread the rumor around. The truth was distorted, you know?

147
00:10:37,459 --> 00:10:38,955
It's true.

148
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:43,120
I'm telling you, you are certainly not Gao Bin's son.

149
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:46,020
As for the illegitimate child rumor, that's not true at all.

150
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:50,640
Then was your conversation with Auntie about me?

151
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,120
Yes, it was.

152
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:57,300
We were saying that the relationship between Gao Bin and your parents was quite good.

153
00:10:57,300 --> 00:10:58,866
Principal Jin,

154
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:01,140
you don't have to act perfunctorily towards me.

155
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:05,779
You can just directly tell me what exactly happened between Mr. Gao and my parents.

156
00:11:05,779 --> 00:11:10,080
I-It's nothing much. It's all in the past.

157
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:23,105
It's all right if you're not willing to tell me.

158
00:11:23,105 --> 00:11:25,520
I'll investigate it on my own.

159
00:11:41,660 --> 00:11:44,740
Stop reading. Stop reading it.

160
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:49,159
I asked you all here for a little meeting to talk about something rather serious.

161
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:53,400
How serious can it be? Which subject did you fail this time?

162
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:57,120
Stop laughing. Be serious.

163
00:11:57,120 --> 00:12:02,179
Grades are nothing compared to this.

164
00:12:02,179 --> 00:12:03,279
How important is it then?

165
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:06,940
Character and personal conduct.

166
00:12:06,940 --> 00:12:08,179
Are you going to pay me back?

167
00:12:08,179 --> 00:12:09,600
Step back.

168
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:12,859
Here's the deal. It's the first time Xiaowen and Mi Jia came to Tieyuan.

169
00:12:12,859 --> 00:12:16,339
We didn't give them a decent present

170
00:12:16,339 --> 00:12:20,140
or even a welcome ceremony. Isn't that embarrassing?

171
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:24,219
Why don't we prepare a small gift for them?

172
00:12:24,219 --> 00:12:28,659
How can it be a small gift? It has to be a big gift! Am I right?

173
00:12:28,659 --> 00:12:33,934
I've made the decision. I'm going to give Xiaowen the same game console that my mom bought me last time.

174
00:12:33,934 --> 00:12:36,000
Do you have money?

175
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,539
You have money.

176
00:12:37,539 --> 00:12:39,659
That's the reason why I've gathered all of you here.

177
00:12:39,659 --> 00:12:43,599
Our little group should help each other.

178
00:12:43,599 --> 00:12:46,140
If you lend me a hand today,

179
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:49,959
I will pay you double someday.

180
00:12:49,959 --> 00:12:52,020
Gao Yang, you haven't even paid me back yet!

181
00:12:52,020 --> 00:12:55,800
Now you want to buy a game console for Xiaowen? How generous of you.

182
00:12:55,800 --> 00:13:00,200
Jiabao, look at you, how can you compare to Xiaowen?

183
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:03,140
He has never played a game console before.

184
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:09,220
I will give him... his entire childhood.

185
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:18,861
Xiaowen, how's your investigation going?

186
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:22,197
I still need to investigate.

187
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:25,359
What exactly happened?

188
00:13:28,870 --> 00:13:31,280
How are you doing at your aunt's place?

189
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:33,919
Really well. Auntie is quite nice to me.

190
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:37,020
There's meat in every meal and she buys me new clothes.

191
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:39,635
That's nice.

192
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:45,866
What about your grades? How are your grades lately?

193
00:13:46,850 --> 00:13:48,541
They're alright.

194
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,502
Can I stop tutoring you?

195
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:55,720
What... what do you mean?

196
00:13:55,720 --> 00:14:00,120
Gao Yang, I support you! I'll lend you 500.

197
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,100
- Are you crazy?
- Have you gone crazy?

198
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:04,960
You guys don't understand. This is the bearing of a man.

199
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:08,119
Look at Beibei. Let's entertain Xiaowen first.

200
00:14:08,119 --> 00:14:10,360
Then we'll warmly welcome Mi Jia.

201
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:12,450
300.

202
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:16,279
300 it is then. Well, let's all go home and get the money.

203
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:19,960
We'll have a small gathering tonight to bond.

204
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,990
Sure.

205
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:23,480
We'll go to your place.

206
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,497
You're coming to my place to bond?

207
00:14:25,497 --> 00:14:29,480
You're so... Fine, I admit defeat.

208
00:14:30,690 --> 00:14:32,519
- Attention, attention!
- Listen.

209
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:36,660
Gao Yang from Class 3, Grade 2 has requested The Hero's Song
- It's here.

210
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:39,100
for his good buddy, Ye Xiaowen.

211
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:40,839
Meanwhile, Gao Yang

212
00:14:40,839 --> 00:14:46,859
wants to invite his good buddy, Ye Xiaowen, to a small gathering at Zhao Jiabao's place tonight.

213
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,595
"Good...

214
00:14:51,810 --> 00:14:53,524
buddy"?

215
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:01,000
♫ The majestic river flows to the East ♫

216
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,840
♫ The stars align with the Big Dipper ♫

217
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:05,939
♫ Align with the Big Dipper ♫

218
00:15:05,939 --> 00:15:08,599
♫ A bowl of wine for sworn brothers ♫

219
00:15:08,599 --> 00:15:10,350
♫ Align— ♫

220
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:15,360
You're home? What do you want for dinner tonight?

221
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,600
What's wrong?

222
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:30,220
- We have a problem.
- What problem?

223
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:33,359
- The child misunderstood us.
- Who misunderstood us?

224
00:15:33,359 --> 00:15:36,339
It's Xiaowen. He came to ask me today.

225
00:15:36,339 --> 00:15:41,099
He asked what Gao Bin's relationship is with his parents.

226
00:15:41,099 --> 00:15:44,900
What should I say? Gao Bin would surely blame me if he finds out.

227
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:49,299
What is there to blame you for? It's something that he did.

228
00:15:49,299 --> 00:15:52,360
Besides, Bin had a crush on Xiaowen's mom for so many years, right?

229
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:55,159
Didn't he argue with Anna over this frequently?

230
00:15:55,159 --> 00:15:57,299
That's true.

231
00:15:57,299 --> 00:16:01,719
But the rumor came from our family.

232
00:16:01,719 --> 00:16:05,179
Wait, what do you mean? Who in our family leaked it out?

233
00:16:05,179 --> 00:16:07,199
Your daughter.

234
00:16:07,199 --> 00:16:10,859
That boorish child. Why does she have such a big mouth?

235
00:16:10,859 --> 00:16:14,400
What should I do? How should I explain it?

236
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:19,439
W-W-Well... If we can't explain it, then don't.

237
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,218
This...

238
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:27,620
Do you remember the year Anna gave birth to Gao Yang? Bin disappeared for a week.

239
00:16:27,620 --> 00:16:31,320
Anna came to our house and cried. She said Bin went to see his old flame.

240
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:33,859
Doesn't that mean he went to visit Wenjing and Xiaowen?

241
00:16:33,859 --> 00:16:35,300
What do you mean by that?

242
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:40,340
Are you saying Xiaowen is really Gao Bin's illegitimate son?

243
00:16:40,340 --> 00:16:41,999
That's not entirely impossible.

244
00:16:41,999 --> 00:16:44,420
What are you saying?

245
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:47,920
I... I'm just kidding.

246
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:53,259
Instead of pulling a long face at home, you should go see Bin at his place

247
00:16:53,259 --> 00:16:57,720
and straighten it out with him. See what he says to the child.

248
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,990
Okay?

249
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:04,940
[Jenny's Salon]

250
00:17:04,940 --> 00:17:07,818
- Xiaowen, here.
[We owe Ye Xiaowen a high-end game console, NDS (Nintendo DS).]

251
00:17:09,260 --> 00:17:13,519
Here's the thing. It's your first time in Tieyuan. We didn't even host a welcoming party for you.

252
00:17:13,519 --> 00:17:16,839
Today, we'll make it up to you.

253
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,160
This is an IOU.

254
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:22,960
[We owe Ye Xiaowen a high-end game console, NDS.]

255
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:25,740
Once I save up enough money, I'll buy you a new one.

256
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:28,759
Thank you. You don't have to.

257
00:17:28,759 --> 00:17:31,900
Just take this for now. Well, I have an announcement to make.

258
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:33,279
Gao Yang, I have something to tell you.

259
00:17:33,279 --> 00:17:36,641
What a coincidence! I have something to tell everyone, too.

260
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,800
Come on, Xiaowen.

261
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:55,600
I, Gao Yang, take you, Ye Xiaowen, as my sworn brother.

262
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:57,519
Though we weren't born on the same day,

263
00:17:57,519 --> 00:18:00,783
I vow to go to college with you on the same day.

264
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:03,860
I was born in July. What about you?

265
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,499
N-N-November.

266
00:18:08,499 --> 00:18:10,058
Call me Big Brother.

267
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,879
Come on, cheers.

268
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:36,100
What's wrong? You don't think it's not ceremonious enough? Fine,

269
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:41,159
we'll just smear blood as a token of oath then.

270
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:46,420
That really hurts. Jiabao.

271
00:18:46,420 --> 00:18:48,219
Bite your own finger! Don't bite mine!

272
00:18:48,219 --> 00:18:49,440
- We're all good buddies!
- Let go of me!

273
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:50,960
- Hurry up.
- Don't bite mine. Bite your own!

274
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:53,140
Gao Yang, are you done playing around?

275
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:57,119
I don't care what you know, but I don't want to be brothers with you.

276
00:18:57,119 --> 00:19:01,139
You don't have to be nice to me either. Just mind your own business.

277
00:19:01,139 --> 00:19:02,659
Wait, Xiaowen.

278
00:19:02,659 --> 00:19:04,680
Hey, Student, why are you leaving?

279
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,599
- I haven't even served the meat dishes yet.
- Exactly.

280
00:19:06,599 --> 00:19:08,019
Thank you, Auntie. I'm leaving now.

281
00:19:08,019 --> 00:19:10,659
Don't go. Are you Xiaowen?

282
00:19:10,659 --> 00:19:12,699
You're staying with Mr. Gao?

283
00:19:12,699 --> 00:19:16,359
Then you mustn't treat yourself as an outsider. Mr. Gao and I used to be neighbors.

284
00:19:16,359 --> 00:19:20,740
We know each other very well! Just make yourself at home.

285
00:19:20,740 --> 00:19:23,780
Auntie, please convince him to stay.

286
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:26,739
Auntie, you used to be Mr. Gao's neighbor?

287
00:19:26,739 --> 00:19:31,759
Of course. We're not living next door now, but when I first came to Tieyuan, we were both living in economic housing.

288
00:19:31,759 --> 00:19:34,960
We lived so close to each other that we were like a family. Am I right, Honey?

289
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:38,200
That's right. At the time, our walls were so thin

290
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:41,319
that when Bin and his wife were fighting, it was as if they were fighting in our house.

291
00:19:41,319 --> 00:19:43,000
There were no secrets between us.

292
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:47,640
Jiabao, serve some drinks to everyone. Dinner will be ready soon. Dinner will be ready soon!

293
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:56,899
Come on, try our cooking.
[Jenny's Salon]

294
00:19:56,899 --> 00:19:58,839
- Eat more. Have some more.
- Okay.

295
00:19:58,839 --> 00:20:01,019
- Uncle, you've worked hard.
- Thanks.

296
00:20:01,019 --> 00:20:03,319
Look at Xiaowen, he's so sensible.

297
00:20:03,319 --> 00:20:05,839
Xiaowen is such a good child. He's very enthusiastic.

298
00:20:05,839 --> 00:20:08,640
Let me tell you, I used to be a big shot too.

299
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:10,119
You've all heard about it, right?

300
00:20:10,119 --> 00:20:13,400
I used to be a famous dance opera artist in Tieyuan.

301
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,759
- That's right.
- My dad told me about it before.

302
00:20:15,759 --> 00:20:22,159
Look at Auntie. Even though her appearance is like this right now, she used to be one of the major local dance opera singers, too.

303
00:20:22,159 --> 00:20:25,160
- That is my mom.
- Let's put on a show for these kids.

304
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:27,340
Come on. I'll play the accompaniment for you.

305
00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:32,200
- Go.
- ♪ New Year is in January ♪

306
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:35,720
♪ On the first day of the New Year ♪

307
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:38,480
- You should give a round of applause!
- That was awesome!

308
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,939
I'm so proud of you!

309
00:20:39,939 --> 00:20:42,659
We haven't sung for years so the note is hard to reach now. But the tone is still there.

310
00:20:42,659 --> 00:20:44,359
It's wonderful. Let's eat.

311
00:20:44,359 --> 00:20:46,039
Uncle, let me give you a toast.

312
00:20:46,039 --> 00:20:49,080
Okay, okay. Come on. Xiaowen.

313
00:20:49,080 --> 00:20:51,799
Xiaowen is trying to get my dad drunk.

314
00:20:51,799 --> 00:20:53,540
He's happy to be my sworn brother.

315
00:20:53,540 --> 00:20:56,559
Try the spareribs. Your Uncle made it. It's delicious.

316
00:20:56,559 --> 00:20:57,799
- Uncle,
- Come on, eat.

317
00:20:57,799 --> 00:21:03,000
I heard you used to be neighbors with Mr. Gao and have always heard them fighting.

318
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,479
What were they fighting about?

319
00:21:05,479 --> 00:21:06,480
It was nothing serious.

320
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:09,259
For our generation, every family fights.

321
00:21:09,259 --> 00:21:10,480
It's different now.

322
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:13,539
At the time, we all got married hastily.

323
00:21:13,539 --> 00:21:15,079
What do you mean?

324
00:21:15,079 --> 00:21:16,519
Do you think we got married hastily?

325
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:19,899
We're an exception. Our marriage was based on true love, right?

326
00:21:19,899 --> 00:21:21,799
I was talking about Gao Bin and Anna.

327
00:21:21,799 --> 00:21:23,480
Gao Yang, you heard about it too, right?

328
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:27,039
In your dad's case, we would call that a flash marriage in today's terms.

329
00:21:27,039 --> 00:21:29,720
I was so close to him and I didn't even know he was in a relationship.

330
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:32,440
Suddenly one day, boom, he got married.

331
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,759
Boom!

332
00:21:33,759 --> 00:21:38,379
Soon after that, kaboom, they had a baby and Gao Yang was born.

333
00:21:38,379 --> 00:21:40,119
You're exaggerating. You can really exaggerate.

334
00:21:40,119 --> 00:21:44,539
But after Gao Yang was born, they had small fights every two days and a big fight every three days.

335
00:21:44,539 --> 00:21:46,680
Am I right? They got physical after they argued.

336
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,639
But... that wasn't my fault.

337
00:21:48,639 --> 00:21:54,560
My mom said there has always been a soft spot in my dad's heart that no one was allowed to touch.

338
00:21:54,560 --> 00:21:56,660
- What's a soft spot?
- How would I know?

339
00:21:56,660 --> 00:21:58,799
I know! I know about this soft spot.

340
00:21:58,799 --> 00:21:59,920
I even saw her picture.

341
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:00,759
Who is it?

342
00:22:00,759 --> 00:22:02,700
Her name was Wen... What was it again? She's really pretty.

343
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:04,821
Wen... what was it?

344
00:22:04,821 --> 00:22:07,000
- You've had too much to drink.
- I barely drank at all.

345
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,599
Why are you talking nonsense to the children?

346
00:22:08,599 --> 00:22:10,759
- What's wrong? Where are we going?
- Come on. Let's go.

347
00:22:10,759 --> 00:22:12,960
- I haven't even started eating yet.
- You guys hurry and eat. Go back to studying after eating.

348
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:15,160
- Jiabao, entertain your friends.
- Come on!

349
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:16,480
What's his soft spot?

350
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:18,279
Just eat your food!

351
00:22:18,279 --> 00:22:19,552
Exactly.

352
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:25,880
- Where are you going?
- I need to use the restroom.

353
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,736
Go out the door and turn right.

354
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:33,920
Mi Jia, is Xiaowen usually that interested in other people's parents?

355
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:37,319
Zhao Jiabao, can't you just shut up and eat?

356
00:22:38,759 --> 00:22:39,839
Any why are you getting involved, too?

357
00:22:39,839 --> 00:22:41,119
Don't you know?

358
00:22:41,119 --> 00:22:42,790
Do I know?

359
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:46,720
I know. You don't know.

360
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:49,340
Gao Yang was there. What nonsense were you saying?

361
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:52,240
I wasn't speaking nonsense. Wasn't it true about Bin back then?

362
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,540
So many people wanted to go on blind dates with him. Why didn't he say yes?

363
00:22:54,540 --> 00:22:56,880
He even refused Anna when she pursued him. Why?

364
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:59,880
Wasn't it because he still had feelings for that Wen... Wenjing?

365
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,240
That's right. I remember now, Wenjing.

366
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:04,219
He was already married for many years yet he still hid a box of pictures of her.

367
00:23:04,219 --> 00:23:06,680
He refused to throw them out when we urged him to. I even helped him stash them before.

368
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,519
How many years has it been?

369
00:23:08,519 --> 00:23:09,880
Bin has been divorced for so long.

370
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,200
Why did you bring that up again?

371
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:14,559
I just wanted to say that Bin has never forgotten his first love.

372
00:23:14,559 --> 00:23:16,599
Which first love of yours did that remind you of?

373
00:23:16,599 --> 00:23:18,119
You are my first love. Let's speak outside.

374
00:23:18,119 --> 00:23:20,440
- Be honest, which first love are you thinking about?
- Don't be so loud.

375
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,640
- Are you hiding a box of pictures, too?
- What could I be hiding?

376
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,975
- Tell me. Hurry up and tell me.
- Even if I were to hide something, it'd be pictures of you.

377
00:23:37,039 --> 00:23:38,534
Bin,

378
00:23:39,079 --> 00:23:42,480
Xiaowen is Wenjing's son.

379
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:46,499
Then you and Wenjing...

380
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,939
Memories of youth.

381
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:56,000
I won't say much about it.

382
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,339
Look at our relationship.

383
00:23:58,339 --> 00:24:00,519
We've been colleagues for 20 years

384
00:24:00,519 --> 00:24:02,359
and neighbors for a dozen years.

385
00:24:02,359 --> 00:24:07,160
If my words make you uncomfortable, don't take it to heart, okay?

386
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:09,739
What do you want to say?

387
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:16,359
Xiaowen had a tough childhood.

388
00:24:16,359 --> 00:24:18,283
He's very sensitive.

389
00:24:18,283 --> 00:24:20,979
You shouldn't keep any secrets from him.

390
00:24:20,979 --> 00:24:22,880
What secrets am I hiding from him?

391
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:25,759
I'm so good to Xiaowen. I treat him like my own son.

392
00:24:25,759 --> 00:24:29,099
You're not planning to tell him about you and Wenjing?

393
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:32,899
Why would I tell him about that?

394
00:24:32,899 --> 00:24:36,560
That was just my impulsiveness and ignorance when I was young.

395
00:24:36,560 --> 00:24:41,280
Besides, if I tell Xiaowen about that, how will I get along with him?

396
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:42,599
Stop talking nonsense!

397
00:24:42,599 --> 00:24:45,240
If I was Xiaowen, I would suspect you, too, you know?

398
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:46,759
Suspect me for what?

399
00:24:46,759 --> 00:24:49,759
I'm telling you. You should explain everything to the child as soon as possible.

400
00:24:49,759 --> 00:24:51,140
That's for your own good.

401
00:24:51,140 --> 00:24:53,240
Explain what?

402
00:24:56,799 --> 00:24:58,792
Let's just drink.

403
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:02,060
What do you mean?

404
00:25:43,530 --> 00:25:46,990
[Track and Field]
[New Practical Dictionary for Student Compositions]

405
00:26:11,179 --> 00:26:13,760
When did Xiaowen leave?

406
00:26:15,140 --> 00:26:18,019
Gao Yang, you've truly grown up.

407
00:26:18,019 --> 00:26:19,838
What do you mean?

408
00:26:19,838 --> 00:26:24,980
Your attitude towards Xiaowen is really mature and manly.

409
00:26:24,980 --> 00:26:30,720
Beibei, when you come across someone who lost both his parents like Xiaowen, everyone should lend him a hand.

410
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,394
That's right.

411
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,504
Lost both his parents?

412
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,019
Isn't Uncle Gao still alive?

413
00:26:38,019 --> 00:26:40,279
What does that have to do with Gao Bin?

414
00:26:40,279 --> 00:26:42,200
Did you look at the note I gave you?

415
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:44,941
What note? Wasn't it a photo sticker?

416
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:48,079
We're totally not on the same page!

417
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:20,440
[Certificate]

418
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:24,520
[Children's Wooden Blocks]

419
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,799
♪ Let's drink ♪

420
00:27:40,799 --> 00:27:44,079
♪ Celebratory wine today ♪

421
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:46,140
♪ Ambitions ♪

422
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,726
Xiaowen,

423
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:52,282
what are you looking for?

424
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:55,699
Are you cold?

425
00:27:56,979 --> 00:27:59,119
I'll find you a jacket to wear.

426
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:02,467
Where did it go?

427
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:05,306
Here it is.

428
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:10,060
They gave me two during the last competition.

429
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:11,599
One for each of us.

430
00:28:11,599 --> 00:28:13,600
Try it on.

431
00:28:13,600 --> 00:28:15,040
Here.

432
00:28:22,359 --> 00:28:23,874
Put it on.

433
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:27,721
I'll try it too and see if it fits.

434
00:28:39,559 --> 00:28:42,759
Gao Yang! Don't be impulsive, Gao Yang!

435
00:28:42,759 --> 00:28:44,839
Calm down! Don't fight with your dad!

436
00:28:44,839 --> 00:28:47,700
Beibei, quickly go home right now, and tightly shut the doors and windows!

437
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:49,284
Wait!

438
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,979
Destiny makes fools of us.

439
00:28:54,599 --> 00:28:56,459
What do you think? You're warm now, right?

440
00:28:56,459 --> 00:28:58,559
What are you guys doing?

441
00:28:58,559 --> 00:29:00,559
Why are you yelling?

442
00:29:00,559 --> 00:29:03,419
- You're home?
- You're even wearing the same jacket, too?

443
00:29:03,419 --> 00:29:04,860
You like it too?

444
00:29:04,860 --> 00:29:06,439
I only have two.

445
00:29:06,439 --> 00:29:09,580
Gao Bin, you've gone too far!

446
00:29:10,359 --> 00:29:11,839
Gao Yang, do you have to go that far?

447
00:29:11,839 --> 00:29:13,240
Isn't it just a jacket?

448
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:14,720
Fine, fine. I'll take mine off for you.

449
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:16,620
Here, here. You can wear it. Put it on.

450
00:29:16,620 --> 00:29:18,279
Who wants your stupid jacket?

451
00:29:18,279 --> 00:29:20,520
You two are ganging up to fool me, is that it?

452
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:24,979
No wonder you made up some excuse a while ago and even told me to be nice to him.

453
00:29:24,979 --> 00:29:27,019
I finally understand now.

454
00:29:27,019 --> 00:29:29,580
I'm the outsider in this house!

455
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:30,920
Why are you making a scene?

456
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:32,060
What did I tell you?

457
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:35,040
You're still trying to make up excuses. What exactly is going on?

458
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:37,060
What is this about?

459
00:29:37,060 --> 00:29:38,759
Mr. Gao, just say it.

460
00:29:38,759 --> 00:29:40,279
Say what?

461
00:29:40,279 --> 00:29:42,319
You're still not going to admit it?

462
00:29:42,319 --> 00:29:43,559
Don't blame me then, Gao Bin.

463
00:29:43,559 --> 00:29:45,160
Wait, what am I supposed to admit?

464
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,659
Fine, Gao Bin.

465
00:29:46,659 --> 00:29:48,679
We've come to this point now!

466
00:29:48,679 --> 00:29:53,100
- Don't blame me for not leaving you some face!
- Hurry up and just say it.

467
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:57,819
Ye Xiaowen is your illegitimate son!

468
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:18,557
You're ashamed of it too, right? Are you feeling guilty now?

469
00:30:19,839 --> 00:30:23,340
Wait, what gave you that idea?

470
00:30:23,340 --> 00:30:25,380
How could Xiaowen be my son?

471
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:27,300
Who blindly spread that rumor?

472
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:29,160
You're still denying it?

473
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:32,699
That's enough. Gao Yang, stop joking around.

474
00:30:32,699 --> 00:30:34,700
Are you crazy?

475
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:37,520
Open your eyes and look carefully!

476
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:40,549
Do we look alike?

477
00:30:47,119 --> 00:30:48,975
Yes, you do!

478
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:52,900
Oh no, this child... has completely gone crazy!

479
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:54,759
Xiaowen, you're a sensible child.

480
00:30:54,759 --> 00:30:56,570
Put some sense into him.

481
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:11,496
Mr. Gao, I would also like to know if your relationship with my parents were simply just friends.

482
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,834
What's going on with you two today?

483
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:20,160
Gao Yang has gone crazy.

484
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:23,004
Xiaowen, you're usually very sensible. Are...

485
00:31:23,004 --> 00:31:25,820
Are you suspecting me too?

486
00:31:33,574 --> 00:31:36,739
Then let's go to the hospital now to get a DNA test. Let's go.

487
00:31:36,739 --> 00:31:38,640
You're still putting up an act? Continue acting then.

488
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:41,400
You both must be addicted to acting, is that it?

489
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:45,519
Move. Come on, you tell me. What exactly is going on?

490
00:31:45,519 --> 00:31:47,200
- Let go of him!
- Let go of me!

491
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:49,039
- Let go of him first!
- Let go of me first!

492
00:31:49,039 --> 00:31:50,640
- Let go of him first!
- I won't!

493
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,480
I'm your dad! Will you listen to me?

494
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:55,160
Bah! You're not my dad!

495
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:57,540
You were unfaithful to my mom! You're shameless!

496
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:59,859
Who are you calling shameless?

497
00:31:59,859 --> 00:32:02,039
- Gao Bin was unfaithful!
- I wasn't!

498
00:32:02,039 --> 00:32:03,319
Gao Bin was unfaithful!

499
00:32:03,319 --> 00:32:04,720
No, I wasn't!

500
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,559
Gao Bin was unfaithful!

501
00:32:06,559 --> 00:32:07,880
Stop saying nonsense! I...

502
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:09,240
Old Jin!

503
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:11,720
Quickly come here and be the judge!

504
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:14,160
I wasn't! Stop saying nonsense!

505
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,079
Gao Yang!

506
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:18,300
Stop saying nonsense!

507
00:32:18,300 --> 00:32:19,919
Old Jin! Old Jin!

508
00:32:19,919 --> 00:32:22,239
I wasn't! Stop saying nonsense!

509
00:32:22,239 --> 00:32:25,119
- Gao Bin!
- I wasn't! Stop saying that!

510
00:32:25,119 --> 00:32:26,079
Gao Yang!

511
00:32:26,079 --> 00:32:28,280
You cheated on my mom!

512
00:32:28,979 --> 00:32:30,619
Xiaowen!

513
00:32:31,759 --> 00:32:33,160
That's right. Go on. Go ahead.

514
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:36,319
Yes, go after your illegitimate son!

515
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:46,820
Gao Yang, I can explain this...

516
00:32:47,319 --> 00:32:49,680
You were unfaithful to my mom!

517
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:52,139
Let me tell you, I, Gao Bin, have a clear conscience!

518
00:32:52,139 --> 00:32:54,759
You have a clear conscience? You're disgusting!

519
00:32:54,759 --> 00:32:55,920
Where are you going?

520
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:58,119
I don't want to see you!

521
00:32:59,319 --> 00:33:02,060
All right. Stop it, will you?

522
00:33:04,240 --> 00:33:07,480
I admit it. At that time,

523
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:11,240
I indeed had feelings for Xiaowen's mom.

524
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,880
That's right!

525
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,979
If you didn't, where would the son come from?

526
00:33:14,979 --> 00:33:18,499
Bro, it was a one-sided crush! A one-sided crush, do you understand?

527
00:33:18,499 --> 00:33:23,040
His mom and I... We were... were purely just friends!

528
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:24,720
I was afraid your mom would misunderstand.

529
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:28,459
After we took this picture, we never contacted each other.

530
00:33:28,459 --> 00:33:30,299
I only found out

531
00:33:30,939 --> 00:33:33,040
something happened to their family a few years ago.

532
00:33:33,759 --> 00:33:38,200
Gao Bin, do you even believe your own words?

533
00:33:40,800 --> 00:33:43,747
- You don't believe me?
- I don't believe you.

534
00:33:43,747 --> 00:33:47,320
Fine, I'll put down all my pride today!

535
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:48,600
- Come here.
- What do you want?

536
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:50,039
Come here!

537
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:52,000
Go ahead. Speak! Lie! Continue lying!

538
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,519
Call your mom!

539
00:33:53,519 --> 00:33:55,259
Your mom knows about me and Xiaowen's mom, too!

540
00:33:55,259 --> 00:33:59,019
Ask her if Ye Xiaowen is my son or not!

541
00:33:59,519 --> 00:34:01,141
Call her!

542
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:26,640
Auntie, I'm home.

543
00:34:26,640 --> 00:34:28,719
- Jia'er, you're home.
- Yes.

544
00:34:29,559 --> 00:34:31,599
Did you have a good dinner at your classmate's house?

545
00:34:31,599 --> 00:34:33,276
It was delicious.

546
00:34:34,119 --> 00:34:36,220
I'm so stuffed now.

547
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:39,539
Come on.

548
00:34:39,539 --> 00:34:41,311
Jia'er, come here.

549
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:46,480
- What is it?
- I have something for you.

550
00:34:48,159 --> 00:34:51,139
Put this on. It'll help you get into a good college.

551
00:34:51,139 --> 00:34:53,060
A-A-Auntie, t-t-this is t-too expensive.

552
00:34:53,060 --> 00:34:55,579
I-I-I can't accept it.

553
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:58,939
I don't have any children.

554
00:34:58,939 --> 00:35:01,939
For so many years, I didn't even have someone to accompany me.

555
00:35:01,939 --> 00:35:04,559
You're my only family.

556
00:35:04,559 --> 00:35:06,979
Nothing is more precious than you.

557
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:09,331
Take it.

558
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:18,299
Don't you s-still have my dad?

559
00:35:18,299 --> 00:35:20,579
Don't mention him.

560
00:35:20,579 --> 00:35:22,680
He's heartless.

561
00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:28,159
Back then, yes, he was young and had you out of wedlock.

562
00:35:28,159 --> 00:35:32,860
But he shouldn't have abandoned you and ran away without telling me.

563
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:35,619
Tell me. Is that something a human being would do?

564
00:35:35,619 --> 00:35:38,860
I gave up on him a long time ago.

565
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:41,980
I've cut off contact with him for years.

566
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:46,939
I only wanted to find you.

567
00:35:46,939 --> 00:35:49,299
My efforts paid off.

568
00:35:49,299 --> 00:35:55,420
We have to thank Mr. Gao for allowing us to reunite again.

569
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,634
Put it on.

570
00:36:03,939 --> 00:36:06,279
Who is it?

571
00:36:06,279 --> 00:36:09,839
- I-I'll go take a look.
- Okay.

572
00:36:20,319 --> 00:36:23,960
Step on it!

573
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:27,100
Can you stop moving around back there? I can't ride fast that way.

574
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:29,320
Aren't you a PE teacher? You have such weak stamina.

575
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:31,919
Hurry, Xiaowen disappeared!

576
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,440
I can't anymore, Gao Yang.

577
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,619
You're too heavy.

578
00:36:39,619 --> 00:36:41,660
Get off and push.

579
00:36:47,619 --> 00:36:50,780
Xiaowen, why are you here so late?

580
00:37:02,119 --> 00:37:04,419
Stay at your aunt's house.

581
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:08,252
Don't forget to train

582
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:10,892
and don't fall behind in class.

583
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:14,674
Wait, wh-wh-what happened to you?

584
00:37:14,674 --> 00:37:15,960
I'm going to leave Tieyuan.

585
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,440
Wh-Wh-Why...

586
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:21,119
Wh-Wh-Why?

587
00:37:21,119 --> 00:37:22,658
Don't be anxious.

588
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:25,260
Don't be anxious, whether I'm here or not.

589
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:27,560
Your auntie is a kind person.

590
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:29,120
You can trust her.

591
00:37:29,120 --> 00:37:30,599
B-B-But X-X-Xiaowen,

592
00:37:30,599 --> 00:37:33,320
I-I-I...

593
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:35,480
- If you leave, I-I...
- I'll come back to visit you.

594
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:38,800
Xiaowen! Xiaowen!

595
00:37:39,494 --> 00:37:41,199
- Gao Bin, I caught him!
- Don't let him go! I'm coming!

596
00:37:41,199 --> 00:37:42,920
- Let go! Let go of me!
- It was all a misunderstanding!

597
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:43,840
- Let go of me!
- It was just a misunderstanding!

598
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,802
It was just a misunderstanding, Xiaowen!

599
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:50,749
Xiaowen, it was just a misunderstanding!

600
00:37:54,855 --> 00:37:56,440
Xiaowen, it was our fault.

601
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:59,519
- I beg you, please don't leave Tieyuan!
- I beg you, please don't leave Tieyuan!

602
00:38:22,510 --> 00:38:27,560
''Wings to Fly to the Future'' - Yang Feitong

603
00:38:27,565 --> 00:38:33,513
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

604
00:38:33,513 --> 00:38:40,810
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

605
00:38:40,810 --> 00:38:46,868
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

606
00:38:46,868 --> 00:38:52,908
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

607
00:38:52,908 --> 00:38:59,260
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

608
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:05,100
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

609
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:09,087
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

610
00:39:09,087 --> 00:39:12,535
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

611
00:39:12,535 --> 00:39:15,830
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

612
00:39:15,830 --> 00:39:22,590
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

613
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:25,801
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

614
00:39:25,801 --> 00:39:30,013
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

615
00:39:30,013 --> 00:39:33,733
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

616
00:39:33,733 --> 00:39:41,693
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
